  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/1d030019416038ecee0c7916b9f86a07.avif?t=1721608884\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br>This work brings the second adventure of the strange superhero \"Blowfly\"! You'll continue to use your protagonist's flying and dash abilities to progress through a series of hand-crafted precision platforming levels. Richer level mechanisms and more distinctive enemy types will bring more unknowns and challenges to your adventure!<br>This time, Blowfly will go deep into the enemy's lair and completely destroy the Assman's evil plan!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/320bac0d5b98bd34479e4bee33d747f2.apng?t=1721608884\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/320bac0d5b98bd34479e4bee33d747f2.poster.avif?t=1721608884\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=336 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.apng?t=1721608884\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.poster.avif?t=1721608884\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Challenge 40 precisely crafted handmade platform levels!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.apng?t=1721608884\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.poster.avif?t=1721608884\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Battle against foolish yet formidable Asmans!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.apng?t=1721608884\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.poster.avif?t=1721608884\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Speedrun Challenge! Earn time and poop medals for each level!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.apng?t=1721608884\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.poster.avif?t=1721608884\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Take on unique and powerful bosses!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.apng?t=1721608884\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.poster.avif?t=1721608884\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Assist the superhero in completing their world-saving mission!</h2>",
