st foolish yet formidable Asmans!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.apng?t=1721608884\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.poster.avif?t=1721608884\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Speedrun Challenge! Earn time and poop medals for each level!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.apng?t=1721608884\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.poster.avif?t=1721608884\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Take on unique and powerful bosses!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.apng?t=1721608884\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831590/extras/a983986b84b4a38264f1f444a4f7eb74.poster.avif?t=1721608884\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> Assist the superhero in completing their world-saving mission!</h2>",
